 * âœ“ 5. MQTT BROKER SETUP:
 *       You need a running MQTT broker (Mosquitto, HiveMQ, etc.)
 *       Install Mosquitto on Linux: sudo apt-get install mosquitto
 *       Test with: mosquitto_sub -h BROKER_IP -t greenhouse/sensor_data
