 * ============================================================================
 * TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE
 * ============================================================================
 * 
 * âŒ "MQTT publish failed - payload may be too large"
 *    â†’ Buffer size is set to 1024 bytes. If still failing, increase further:
 *      mqttClient.setBufferSize(2048);
